\"><strong>大嬸</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MW2jQOx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMW2jQOx.gif&h=134e15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">值得留意的是<br />\n可幸的是解像度不高、兼汪小姐白哲肌膚<br />\n綺夢未能喧賓奪主</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57DzGCZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57DzGCZ.png&h=0d2b3785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tkeYXId.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtkeYXId.png&h=cb11348f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多謝各位支持!!!!<br />\n(阿姐腋下依然白滑)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/aogvuzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Faogvuzy.jpg&h=27dab105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ASWrttT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FASWrttT.jpg&h=96fe1fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fUuCYEe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfUuCYEe.jpg&h=49d2ccc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">各位觀眾~~綺夢!!!!!!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YEW02HU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYEW02HU.png&h=b345a876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dQIrt9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdQIrt9i.png&h=16c4285a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0WeVNgj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0WeVNgj.png&h=e83656db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20091121/large/21ec2p5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20091121%2Flarge%2F21ec2p5a.jpg&h=8c0079d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCdEHqp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCdEHqp.gif&h=afb3860e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿姐承認腋下有綺夢，但否認沒有剃腋毛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/H8EdOC3CWJEbvhtzr5iRtfRQDk8=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IIJHRQP5GRARSLT7AKNHVLRHVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FH8EdOC3CWJEbvhtzr5iRtfRQDk8%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIIJHRQP5GRARSLT7AKNHVLRHVU.jpg&h=2cc3f032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/ftp/News/20200406/HK/_f3e0574dfe5ea5eb8eaa7c6fd2c3de55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Ftor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20200406%2FHK%2F_f3e0574dfe5ea5eb8eaa7c6fd2c3de55.jpg&h=9e32e161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿姐一定用咗自己嘅品牌先至咁白滑!!!!<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/c13840.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fc13840.gif&h=f7096b8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d98c01190000a7d39d0d5437f1074d3019bf767e","tid":2163452,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>【肺炎天使】汪 明 荃 小 姐 悉 心 打 扮 攜 帶 兩 大 卷 廁 紙 娛 樂 大 家<p class=\"center\"><br />\n貴為平安鐘大使嘅汪明荃小姐衣飾簡約美麗<br />\n宛如下凡拯救世人嘅天使般純潔善良<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHXGaB3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHXGaB3.jpg&h=381564a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心口掛住雪白無瑕嘅平安鐘與白綿綿嘅紙巾格外匹配<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eH86mJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeH86mJK.jpg&h=73e60e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有俊男相伴 阿姐更顯仙露明珠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6